summary:
hello tumblr! im starting an art blog, so here’s my welcome!
my name is ren, and i go by she/he/they pronouns. so anything’s...
body:
hello tumblr! im starting an art blog, so here’s my welcome!


my name is ren, and i go by she/he/they pronouns. so anything’s fine! i’m not bothered by any misgendering, it happens all the time haha


i’m self taught, and in my teenage years. i just look at others work, than mine, and see what i have to improve! i try to find all my flaws and fix them. constructive criticism is greatly appreciated! <3


i’ll have posts queued every wednesday, sunday, and saturday! but i’ll post between then too. those are just set schedules.


requests are needed! request all you want.
